## Service Worker Strategy

### Caching Approach
- **Cache-first:** Static assets (JS, CSS, images)
- **Network-first:** Level data (allows updates)
- **Stale-while-revalidate:** Icons, fonts

### sw.js Implementation
```javascript
const CACHE_VERSION = 'v1';
const STATIC_CACHE = `static-${CACHE_VERSION}`;

const STATIC_ASSETS = [
  '/',
  '/index.html',
  '/shared/meta.js',
  '/shared/storage.js',
  '/shared/daily.js',
  '/shared/audio.js',
  '/shared/history.js',
  '/shared/rng.js',
  '/styles/reset.css',
  '/styles/variables.css',
  '/styles/game-shell.css',
  '/games/water-sort/index.html',
  '/games/water-sort/game.js',
  '/games/water-sort/renderer.js',
  '/games/water-sort/levels.json',
  // ... all game files
];

self.addEventListener('install', (event) => {
  event.waitUntil(
    caches.open(STATIC_CACHE)
      .then(cache => cache.addAll(STATIC_ASSETS))
      .then(() => self.skipWaiting())
  );
});

self.addEventListener('activate', (event) => {
  event.waitUntil(
    caches.keys().then(keys => {
      return Promise.all(
        keys.filter(key => key !== STATIC_CACHE)
            .map(key => caches.delete(key))
      );
    }).then(() => self.clients.claim())
  );
});

self.addEventListener('fetch', (event) => {
  event.respondWith(
    caches.match(event.request)
      .then(cached => cached || fetch(event.request))
      .catch(() => caches.match('/offline.html'))
  );
});
```

